---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">

    <div class="footer-brand">
      <div class="logo">macomo<span class="dot">·</span>note</div>
      <p class="brand-desc">お金と子育てと学びのある、整う暮らし。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-column">
        <h3>人気記事</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/blog/asset-3000man/">資産3,000万円までの道のり</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/kakei-kokai-2026-04/">家計管理のリアル</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/boki3-benkyoho/">子育てしながら勉強するコツ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-column">
        <h3>カテゴリー</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/blog/">お金</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/">子育て</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/">学び</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-column">
        <h3>運営情報</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/about">プロフィール</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">お問い合わせ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>© {year} macomo note</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-top: 80px;
    background: var(--color-paper);
    padding: 56px 24px 32px;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    max-width: var(--layout-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Brand */
  .footer-brand {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .dot { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .brand-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-ink-mute);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* Grid */
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .footer-column h3 {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink-mute);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .footer-column ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .footer-column a {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--duration-base) var(--easing-standard);
  }
  .footer-column a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  /* Bottom */
  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink-mute);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
